folder: North Hempstead Turn & 164th Street, Queens, NY
text:
North Hempstead Turnpike, at the N.E. corner of 164th Street (Renwick Ave.), showing the Fisher house which was moved to this site from another which the collector does not designate. The house faces Renwick Avenue (Jamaica trolley line thereon). This is a set of two views, viewed in opposite directions.

July 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
title: Queens: North Hempstead Turn - 164th Street
